at one time the Fortunate One was dwelling near lavī
in the domicile of the yakkha lavaka
Then the yakkha lavaka approached the Fortunate One
and after approaching he said this to the Fortunate One
Get out ascetic
Yes friend said the Fortunate One and he got out
Go in ascetic
Yes friend said the Fortunate One and he went in
