Sixty Abbreviated Texts
The Exterior and Whats NotSelf in the Three Times
Mendicants in the past  future  present sights sounds smells tastes touches and thoughts are notself
And whats notself should be truly seen with right understanding like this This is not mine I am not this this is not my self 
