And what is a duality
Its just the eye and sights the ear and sounds the nose and smells the tongue and tastes the body and touches and the mind and thoughts
This is called a duality
Mendicants suppose someone was to say
Ill reject this duality and describe another duality Theyd have no grounds for that
theyd be stumped by questions and in addition theyd get frustrated
Why is that
Because theyre out of their element
